# ==========================================
# GDG Hackathon / Firebase Configuration
# ==========================================
# Normally, we would ignore google-services.json to protect API keys.
# However, for the GDG Hackathon, we are explicitly NOT ignoring it 
# so that judges can easily clone, build, and evaluate the application 
# without needing to configure their own Firebase project.
# 
# !android/app/google-services.json
